Process the TETCs variables:

ds <- d %>% 
    select(Q11_1:Q11_12) %>% 
    set_names(1:12) %>% 
    mutate_all(str_extract, "\\(?[0-9,.]+\\)?") %>% 
    mutate_all(as.integer) %>% 
    set_names(str_c("v", 1:12))

Perhaps a three profile solution:

plot_profiles_mplus(x, to_center = TRUE)
